Singer, Songwriter Post Malone released his single “Wow,” in December 2018 and its been making rounds on Billboard Hot 100 and has even been in the top 10. The artist is back with a new remix which features Tyga and Roddy Ricch. The remix allowed for both Tyga and Ricch to have enough room to leave their own impression on the beat which they did quite well. Listen to “Wow” Remix via YouTube below;